title: DIRECTV by EnterSource / NewsRadio WGNS Week 8 Awards Presented
text:
DIRECTV by EnterSource / NewsRadio WGNS Week 8 Awards Presented Published: October 15, 2015 
Middle Tennessee Christian School's win over Cannon County in week 8 of the prep football season garnered them the DIRECTV by EnterSource / NewsRadio WGNS "Game of the Week" award. 
Andy DeGraw, Vice President of DIRECTV by EnterSource, presented a plaque to the Cougars Wednesday. 
The game's MVP was running back Tanner Green. He had 251 rushing yards and three rushing touchdowns in the win over the Lions. Congratulations to MTCS and Tanner Green from NewsRadio WGNS and DIRECTV by EnterSource. Related Articles
